snippet.description:
@TSeriesBhaktiMarathi Presents:- Celebrate the divine blessings of Lord Ganesha with this spiritually uplifting Angaraki Special Ganpati Bhaktigeete Audio Jukebox, featuring timeless and soul-stirring devotional songs by the legendary Anuradha Paudwal along with various renowned artists.
#AngarakiSpecial #GanpatiGeete #TSeriesBhaktiMarathi

‚ñ∫ Hey Ganraya Tula ‚óÑ 0:00:00

‚ñ∫ Karunakara Lambodara ‚óÑ 0:09:19
‚ñ∫ Laadacha Majha Ganpati ‚óÑ 0:15:16

--------------------------------------------------------------------------  

Specially curated for Angaraki Chaturthi, this devotional collection is perfect for Ganpati Puja, Sankashti Chaturthi, Ganesh Chaturthi, Aarti, Naam Smaran, and daily Ganesh worship. The melodious bhajans and traditional compositions invoke peace, positivity, and the blessings of Vighnaharta Ganpati.

Let these sacred Ganpati geete fill your home with devotion, faith, and divine energy.
